Run Script:
$ sh 100-display-manager-and-desktop.sh

AUR Installs:
$ yay lightdm-webkit-theme-aether sublime-text-dev nerd-fonts-mononoki slack-desktop balena-etcher

Copy Fish config
$ cp config.fish ~/.config/fish/config.fish

Set LOGIN:
$ sudo systemctl enable lightdm.service

Common Commands:
$ trash-empty							        // self-explanitory
$ sudo pacman -Qtdq | sudo pacman -Rns -		// delete orphan packages
